&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Semantic Data Layer - creating curated, consistent and reliable datasets that enable analytics, reporting and decision making&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Contribute to the design, build and maintenance of robust data pipelines (batch, streaming and replication) that power analytics, reporting and compliance use-cases&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
